<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <%- include('./partials/head.ejs', {
        pageTitle: 'About | Harmony Wellness Group, Tampa FL',
        pageDescription: 'Learn about Harmony Wellness Group—our philosophy, team approach, and commitment to your recovery.'
  }) %>

<body class="flex flex-col min-h-screen antialiased">
  <%- include('./partials/nav.ejs', { navVariant: 'solid' }) %>

  <main class="flex-grow bg-gradient-to-b from-teal-50 via-white to-green-100">
  <!-- Hero / Heading (full width) -->

<!-- Content + Sidebar grid -->
<section class="mx-auto px-6 pb-16 max-w-7xl grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-[2fr_1fr] lg:gap-12">
  <!-- Left: Main content (2/3) -->
  <div class="space-y-8">

    
<h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900">About Harmony Wellness Group</h1>

    <article class="bg-white/95 rounded-2xl shadow p-6 md:p-8 space-y-5 text-gray-700 leading-7">
      <p>Harmony Wellness Group is a modern rehabilitation and wellness clinic dedicated to helping you move,
        heal, and feel your best. We combine evidence-based care with a calm, supportive environment—so recovery
        feels reassuring from the moment you walk in.</p>
      <p>Our team collaborates across disciplines to personalize your plan, whether you’re healing from an injury,
        managing chronic pain, or aiming to improve mobility and performance. We focus on practical progress,
        clear communication, and sustainable results.</p>
      <p>From your first assessment to your final session, we meet you where you are and guide you forward—one step at a time.</p>
    </article>

    <section class="bg-white/95 rounded-2xl shadow p-6 md:p-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">Our Care Philosophy</h2>
      <ul class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-3 text-gray-800">
        <li class="rounded-xl bg-gray-50 p-4 shadow-sm"><strong>Patient-First</strong> — Your goals drive the plan.</li>
        <li class="rounded-xl bg-gray-50 p-4 shadow-sm"><strong>Evidence-Based</strong> — Methods rooted in research.</li>
        <li class="rounded-xl bg-gray-50 p-4 shadow-sm"><strong>Collaborative</strong> — Clinicians who listen and adapt.</li>
        <li class="rounded-xl bg-gray-50 p-4 shadow-sm"><strong>Sustainable</strong> — Progress you can maintain.</li>
      </ul>

      <div class="mt-6">
        <a href="/request-appointment"
           class="inline-block px-5 py-3 bg-teal-700 hover:bg-teal-600 text-white rounded-xl transition">
          Request an Appointment
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>

  <!-- Right: Sidebar (1/3) -->
  <aside class="mt-8 lg:mt-0">
    <div class="bg-white/95 rounded-2xl shadow p-6 space-y-5 lg:sticky lg:top-24">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900">Visit Us</h2>

      <div class="text-sm text-gray-700">
        <p class="font-medium">Harmony Wellness Group</p>
        <p>3709 W Hamilton Ave STE 1, Tampa, FL 33614</p>
        <p class="mt-1">
          <a href="tel:+18135551234" class="text-teal-700 hover:underline">(813) 284-6439</a>
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="rounded-xl overflow-hidden border border-gray-200">
        <iframe
          src="https://www.google.com/maps?q=Harmony%20Wellness%20Group%20Tampa&output=embed"
          width="100%" height="220" style="border:0;" loading="lazy"
          referrerpolicy="no-referrer-when-downgrade"
          aria-label="Map to Harmony Wellness Group"></iframe>
      </div>

      <div class="border-t border-gray-200 pt-4 text-sm text-gray-700">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-y-1">
          <span>Mon–Thu</span><span class="text-right">10:00–6:00</span>
          <span>Fri</span><span class="text-right">10:00–4:00</span>
          <span>Sat</span><span class="text-right">Closed</span>
          <span>Sun</span><span class="text-right">Closed</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <a href="https://maps.google.com/?q=Harmony%20Wellness%20Group%20Tampa"
         target="_blank" rel="noopener"
         class="block text-center px-4 py-2 rounded-lg bg-gray-900 text-white hover:bg-gray-800">
        Get Directions
      </a>
    </div>
  </aside>
</section>
</main>

  <%- include('./partials/footer.ejs') %>
</body>
</html>